@startuml
title Add Candidate - UC1002

actor Operator as "Operator"

participant System

' Step 1: Operator requests to add a new candidate
Operator -> System: 1. Requests to add a new candidate
System --> Operator: 1.1 Displays form for candidate details

' Step 2: Operator provides candidate details
Operator -> System: 2. Enters candidate's details (username, password, first name, last name, email, phone)
System --> Operator: 2.1 Confirms receipt of candidate details

' Step 3: System verifies authorization
System -> System: 3. Verifies authorization (authorization check)

' Step 4: System creates a new system user and candidate
System -> System: 4. Registers a new system user
System -> System: 5. Adds new candidate to the repository

' Step 5: Confirmation of successful candidate creation
System --> Operator: 6. Confirms successful candidate creation

@enduml
